data.description: Great brick home in a great neighborhood. Hardwood floors in living rm and both bedrooms on main level, which includes laundry room, third bedroom is in basement. Granite countertops in kitchen with a quartz backsplash, including a wall oven and a butcher block island, great for food preparation and extra counterspace. Slate tiles in second bath with lots of tile in master bath. A wood deck overlooks a large, fenced backyard, add a spacious porch in front that oversees a tree-lined neighborhood. Great for
data.whatILove: I built a fence in the backyard, had gravel laid and put in 2 flower beds that grow beautiful flowers annually!With a gated wooden fence that guarantees privacy, I call the entire back yard my garden paradise!
